The '''''De Oude Emigrant''''' was the first [[newspaper]] to appear in the [[South African Republic|Transvaal]]. It was first published on 15 October 1859 in [[Potchefstroom]] but lasted only two years before closing down after controversy about its content.<ref name="Fourie2001">{{cite book|last=Fourie|first=Pieter Jacobus |title=Media Studies: Institutions, theories, and issues|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XsTSXIhG2sgC&pg=PA40|year=2001|publisher=Juta Education, p. 40.|isbn=978-0-7021-5655-7}}</ref>

