'''''Home Affairs''''' is a [[South Africa]]n television drama series created and produced by [[Roberta Durrant]]. It tells the story of nine very different women whose lives are interconnected. The women's stories reflect the wide cultural range of South African women. The women each undertake a [[journey of self-discovery]], connecting with each other in various and random ways.
